  "subject": "Code to send CDS request generically",
  "commit_message": "Code to send CDS request generically\n\nThis code implements generic way to send\nrequest to CDS, user just need to provide\naction in bpmn and that {action} will pick\n{actionName}.yaml file, collect parameters from\nit. Those parameters will be resolved using\nexecution object and it'll provide json object\nto AbstractCDSProcessingBB.bpmn.\n\nSigned-off-by: tragait <rahul.tyagi@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I56c0028f5e74368a1440090f1ed13627410f9347\nSigned-off-by: tragait <rahul.tyagi@est.tech>\nIssue-ID: SO-2090\n",
